"- Relative dates: call get_current_time.\n"
"- Do not store secrets (passwords/tokens) in long-term memory.\n"
"- Files with suffixes like .org / .org1 / .org2 are backup copies and "
"must not be treated as primary editable files.\n"
"- If you create Python files, run `python -m py_compile`.\n"
"- If expert-level knowledge is required, use Agent Skills prompt "
